{
  "id": "minimalist-note",
  "name": "极简便签",
  "category": "minimalist",
  "description": "一张极简主义风格的便签，简洁优雅的设计",
  "trigger": {
    "type": "random",
    "probability": 0.03,
    "conditions": [
      {
        "type": "mood",
        "operator": "contains",
        "value": "平静|简约|现代|都市|工作",
        "description": "平静或现代场景可能触发"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variables": {
    "title": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "标题"
    },
    "content": {
      "type": "text",
      "maxLength": 200,
      "description": "便签内容"
    },
    "date": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "日期"
    },
    "priority": {
      "type": "string",
      "default": "普通",
      "options": ["普通", "重要", "紧急"],
      "description": "优先级"
    }
  },
  "promptTemplate": "请生成一张极简便签的内容。\n\n背景信息：\n- 场景：{{scene}}\n- 主题：{{theme}}\n\n要求：\n1. 内容要简洁明了\n2. 语言要直接有效\n3. 避免冗余表达\n4. 字数控制在50-150字之间\n\n请直接输出便签内容，不要有其他说明。",
  "style": {
    "theme": "minimalist",
    "colors": ["#ffffff", "#333333", "#f5f5f5"],
    "mood": "简洁现代"
  },
  "rarity": "common",
  "collectible": true
}